## 📥 Dataset

This project uses the **LA Crime Data (2020–Present)**

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **Source** | Los Angeles Police Department |
| **Link** | [Download from data.gov](https://catalog.data.gov/dataset/crime-data-from-2020-to-present) |
| **Format** | CSV |
| **Size** | 200MB+ (too large for GitHub) |
| **Updated** | Daily |

> ⚠️ **Note:** Dataset is not included in this repository due to its large size.  
> Please download it directly from the link above and place it in the `data/` folder.
